{"tid":1461824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機鐵咁撚貴，點日日入去機場呀屌？","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:55:01.000Z","uid":170534,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"674665bcddad77cc48bd386a844ef1d024de61fd","tid":1461824,"uid":170534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"咁多人發夢時開飯都有問題<br />\n機鐵來回都成兩舊水啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRbkhna.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRbkhna.png&h=e4ac1b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">閘口派 barcode 行動有無得諗？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大陸乜7基建都有事前事後公眾考察團，比人民感受國家既偉大<br />\n咁點解三跑無份？ <br />\n香港人，一定要欣賞偉大既三跑工程<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為你都有份比錢嫁!! 比多幾十蚊就可以令更多香港人親身感受到宏偉既工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1f6068eb26f28245b4c8b0bf3e2a17e96e3a75f3","tid":1461824,"uid":288014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:25:44.000Z","msg":"直接跳入去啦 搞咁多 不合作運動之一"},{"pid":"acd5fe8f263b354cb3497d0ab069fb750bdfa623","tid":1461824,"uid":170534,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"呢個係和理非超合作運動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">p 牌唔好又想抹黑</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d838b90c1e94406ba75720e4f9b821a0731de8e8","tid":1461824,"uid":36441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"點解要搭機鐵？"},{"pid":"8c209996cb13a807dd6bd257796fd2c33790914c","tid":1461824,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"jump"},{"pid":"a1430ee29536375130ee30c4fcf2c2d2c6f52bef","tid":1461824,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:32:50.000Z","msg":"封左個閘口